➜微信上线视频号神器，10秒出片、AI剪辑……有点东西！
http://www.sohu.com/a/424260150_282116	8510
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「短视频平台+专属剪辑工具」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">似乎已成标准公式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">各家争先占坑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尤其近日</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>视频号</strong>在手的腾讯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">推出了剪辑App</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「秒简」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（是因为“秒剪”被注册了吗？）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201013/0dd8ec34a0e941e29185d248d8a011ab.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仅限<strong>iOS用户</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（安卓党骂骂咧咧退出直播间）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一上来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">slogan就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“做视频，很简单”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（但其实潜台词是↓↓↓↓）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甭整那些花里胡哨的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">够用就行啦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201013/9f49112eee374c83b51173cfb3dfa593.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
