<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">首先</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>登陆方式</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就相当清（ji）奇（lei）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201013/798217392f804b54834495a60b191ec6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可直接用微信登陆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也能新建用户</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但其实</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">系统自动关联的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都是微信在线的<strong>视频号</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（所以，建了个寂寞......）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">进入<strong>首页</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是清风扑面的感jio</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">咋眼一看就只有<strong>3个大区域</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">果酱妹倒是要康康做起来是有多简单</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201013/54f45ccf7ca24d13a5a619843261dada.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>1</strong></h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>文字、录音自动成视频</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">这操作</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有两个选项</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">输入<strong>文字</strong>或<strong>录音</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>系统自动生成带配音的视频</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文字最多<strong>500字</strong>，语音最长<strong>1分钟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201013/40c83efa488a4f4dbaf54ba99cea5fd3.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生成后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">视频是酱婶儿的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文字成片的配音是siri内味儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而录音的话<strong>自己的配音会成为旁白</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201013/55cd6782990345d5a806debba28e8f93.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">惊喜的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">录音转译文字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（普通话标准的话）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">准确度近乎<strong>100%</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>双击视频可对文案进行修改</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">整体适合<strong>信息密集型</strong>的短视频制作</p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>2</strong></h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>AI剪辑，一键成片</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">从导入素材开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">系统自动适配</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>歌曲、模板</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">亮点在于</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">特殊的<strong>「歌词」模板</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">套入后<strong>自动生成歌词字幕</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（妥妥的Vlog爱好者的福音）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201013/1a376bc0feb94d06bf01413b83ba257c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问题是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">关于配乐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>只能左右滑动选择</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不能自定义，不能搜索查找</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了文字和贴图这些标配</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还可以插入<strong>微信表情</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">注入灵魂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（▼均来自微信聊天添加的官方表情）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201013/444061b3976c4a35a53790c569e9a4f1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>3</strong></h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>完美适配视频号</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“秒简”生成的视频</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不能一键上传到视频号</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但它最终导出的默认比例</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是视频号的标准画幅大小</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201013/edbd4b447dc44781930372a406068d92.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">截取视频时长</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">调整视频画面、位置</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">排序、旋转、镜像翻转视频</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一切基本操作都可以在<strong>“素材”版块</strong>完成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201013/9dd155c189a740b8bade77cab155738e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后导出视频时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以<strong>直接预览</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以及分享给</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>微信好友</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和收藏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201013/0bb258d25da84f138046832524e19413.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是不是很简单？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但果酱妹认为<strong>过于简单了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">微信想和剪映、快剪、必剪做区别</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但一不小心，好像有点用力过勐了</p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>1</strong></h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>视频效果局限</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">且不和剪映、快剪PK视频特效</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从主打的AI剪辑来看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>效果模板太少了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一共就<strong>23款</strong>花样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且有一半</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>都像PPT</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">↓↓↓↓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201013/c58af5cc995445ff835f02523d521369.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文字和录音成片更惨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只有4个模板可选</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">太抠了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（bushi）</p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>2</strong></h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>文字、录音成片无法剪辑</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">文字以及录音生成的视频</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是<strong>无法进行二次编辑</strong>的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尽管录制中途可停顿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一旦有噪音、念错字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就得<strong>重头来过</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201013/4f02157af8804136a5095c8621494fc2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>总而言之</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">「秒简」物如其名</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">适合<strong>快速传达简单信息</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以及对剪辑要求少的<strong>懒人和小白</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽被普遍传作<strong>“为视频号专属打造”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但「秒简」最大的bug</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是<strong>两者的不打通</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（果酱妹赌五毛）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱做连接的微信</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">铁定有新动作</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">期待就完事了</p>
